    "messageBody": "<div id=\"ygrps-yiv-805438402\">\n<html>\n<head>\n \n \n<title>RE: [junit] Testing GUI Classes with no X-Display</title>\n</head>\n \n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">&gt; </font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">&gt; Has anybody else run into this sort of thing? If so, how did </font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">&gt; you approach</font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">&gt; a soltion?There&#39;s 2 solutions that we&#39;ve used:</font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">install xvfb - x virtual frame buffer. </font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">or use</font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">JDK 1.4 with the </font>\n</p>\n<br>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -Djava.awt.headless=true&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">see <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" HREF=\"http://java.sun.com/products/java-media/2D/forDevelopers/java2dfaq.html#xvfb\">http://java.sun.com/products/java-media/2D/forDevelopers/java2dfaq.html#xvfb</a></font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">Cheers,</font>\n</p>\n\n<p><font SIZE=\"2\">Paul Harding</font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">Principal Software Engineer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Algorithmics Inc.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">pharding@...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 189 Spadina Ave.</font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">(voice) 416-217-4431&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Toronto, Ont. M5T 2C6</font>\n<br><font SIZE=\"2\">(fax) 416-971-6100</font>\n</p>\n\n \n</html></div>", 
